s.replaceAll("\\s", "")

\\s â†’ matches any whitespace character

"" â†’ replaces whitespace with nothing

Effect: removes all spaces in the string

Time Complexity: O(n) â†’ loops through the string once

Space Complexity: O(n) â†’ creates a new string

Output: "JavaDeveloper" â†’ all spaces removed

Works for:

Leading spaces

Trailing spaces

Multiple spaces between words
